<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wave-n">wave <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /weɪv/    美 /wev/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>波 (浪)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A huge wave covered our boat and my younger brother fell into the sea.
巨浪把我们的小船吞噬了，我弟弟掉进了海里。</p><footer>北师大新必修②-5</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>挥手；招手：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>gave</strong> us <strong>a wave</strong> as the bus drove off.
公共汽车开走时，他向我们挥了挥手。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>（活动或感情的）风潮；浪潮：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a wave of</strong> panic / protest
一阵恐慌 / 抗议的浪潮</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(声、光、电等的) 波：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>sound waves</strong>
声波</p></div></div>